Warning: The Garry's Mod addon "Portal Gun - Enhanced Aperture Science Handheld Portal Device" contains a memory leak, and will use up all the Lua Memory within a couple of minutes and crash the game- even when you're not using/haven't got a Portal Gun.
You need to unsubscribe from it.

